{
  "texts": [
    "The source building is located in Turin (Italy), and it is occupied at maximum capacity from Monday to Friday between 8:00 and 18:00.",
    "In addition to the load associated with the HVAC system, in the two office rooms a total electric load (E LOAD) of 0.9 kW for lighting services, appliances and office equipment is measured during the occupancy hours.",
    "The building and the cooling system are modelled in EnergyPlus.",
    "Terminal units within buildings were not modelled.",
    "Consequently, the cooling energy is technically provided to the building by means of the OtherEquipment object in EnergyPlus."
  ]
}